{"title":"Urge Rascas Lightens Up Eco-Friendly 3/4-Shell MTB Helmet for Enduro & eMTB Riders","link":"https://bikerumor.com/urge-rascas-lightens-up-eco-friendly-3-4-shell-mtb-helmet-for-enduro-emtb-riders/","date":1730386318000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Urge Rascas lightweight eco-friendly 3/4-shell mountain bike eMTB helmet\" /></p>\n<p>Urge’s latest Rascas helmet reimagines the moto-inspired 3/4-shell helmet for modern aggressive mountain bike and eMTB riders, now in their most environmentally friendly construction yet. Now possible to make entirely from recycled and renewable materials, this new open-face Rascas delivers extended protection, full ventilation, new low-key graphics, and impressively light weight claims… all at a competitive price.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Urge Rascas eco-friendly 3/4 shell MTB helmet</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Inspired by the extra protection of the open-face Jet-style motorcycle trials helmets of their youth, Urge has been making 3/4-shell enduro helmets since at least 2012 with their RealJet. Reissued on their 10th anniversary, six years ago the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/10th-anniversary-limited-edition-urge-endur-o-matic-real-jet-mountain-bike-helmets/\" target=\"_blank\">RealJet</a> offered extra coverage and retro appeal. But it couldn’t compete with the latest helmets on pretty much any real performance characteristics. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, they decided to build a much more modern 3/4-shell enduro &amp; all-mountain helmet.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_trail-riding-with-goggles-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_trail-riding-with-goggles-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Urge Rascas lightweight eco-friendly 3/4-shell mountain bike eMTB helmet, riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_trail-riding-with-goggles-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_trail-riding-with-goggles-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_trail-riding-with-goggles-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_trail-riding-with-goggles-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_trail-riding-with-goggles-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_trail-riding-with-goggles-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_trail-riding-with-goggles-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photos/Urge)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Their new Rascas is fully-vented for maximum airflow and plenty of summer ride cooling with 3 front-facing, 3 top &amp; 4 rear vents, plus large ear openings. Then it gets Urge’s ERT pads to isolate the rider’s head from rotational &amp; linear impact forces, even at lower speeds. And tops it off with a soft padded and moisture-wicking bamboo lining for comfort.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And it does all that at impressive weights less than half of the old RealJet. From a claimed 420-480g depending on size, this could be one of the lightest 3/4 shell enduro helmets out there.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Eco-friendly construction</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_jumping-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_jumping-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Urge Rascas lightweight eco-friendly 3/4-shell mountain bike eMTB helmet, jumping\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_jumping-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_jumping-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_jumping-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_jumping-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_jumping-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_jumping-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_jumping-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Often one of the most unique and interesting features of many Urge helmets, is their use of alternative, more environmentally-friendly materials than we are used to seeing – while still providing safe &amp; affordable protection.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_environmentally-friendly-recycled-materials-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1706\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_environmentally-friendly-recycled-materials-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Urge Rascas lightweight eco-friendly 3/4-shell mountain bike eMTB helmet, recycled content\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_environmentally-friendly-recycled-materials-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_environmentally-friendly-recycled-materials-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_environmentally-friendly-recycled-materials-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_environmentally-friendly-recycled-materials-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_environmentally-friendly-recycled-materials-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_environmentally-friendly-recycled-materials-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_environmentally-friendly-recycled-materials-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_environmentally-friendly-recycled-materials-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The newest bit of eco-friendly tech in this all-new Urge Rascas helmet is its fully recycled polycarbonate shell. Creating the outer PC shell of an in-mold helmet out of recycled material has taken many years for Urge to figure out. And the Rascas is their first helmet to do it, finally meaning they say the helmet can made entirely of recycled or renewable bio-based materials. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-views-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-views-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Urge Rascas lightweight eco-friendly 3/4-shell mountain bike eMTB helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-views-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-views-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-views-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-views-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-views-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-views-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-views-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Recycled polycarbonate does limit possible color choices, so for now Urge can only offer the Rascas in 1 color as fully made of recycled content – in Dark Moon. That color name comes from how the almost black helmet reflects dark blue under direct sunlight – the color coming from the recycled plastic bottles used to make the material.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides its shell, all colors of the Urge Rascas mountain bike helmet feature post-industrial recovered EPS foam, recycled polyamide visors, recycled ABS for its plastic hardware, recycled PET for the straps, and rapidly renewable bamboo lining pads.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_all-sides-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_all-sides-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Urge Rascas lightweight eco-friendly 3/4-shell mountain bike eMTB helmet, studio views\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_all-sides-jpg.webp 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_all-sides-297x119.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_all-sides-1536x614.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_all-sides-120x48.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_all-sides-768x307.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>100% made of recycled materials (in almost black Dark Moon, only)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>light in-mold EPS foam with a recycled polycarbonate (PC) shell</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_ERT-tech-details-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_ERT-tech-details-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Urge Rascas lightweight eco-friendly 3/4-shell mountain bike eMTB helmet, ERT impact protection inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_ERT-tech-details-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_ERT-tech-details-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_ERT-tech-details-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_ERT-tech-details-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_ERT-tech-details-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>soft blue Energy Reduction Technology (<a href=\"https://urgebike.com/en/technologies/\" target=\"_blank\">ERT</a>) lattice polymer pads dissipate rotational &amp; linear impact forces</li>\n\n\n\n<li>altogether natural bamboo fiber padding</li>\n\n\n\n<li>FidLock chin strap buckle, held in place by magnets</li>\n\n\n\n<li>dial-adjust rear retention system</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-with-Pop-Off-visor-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-with-Pop-Off-visor-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Urge Rascas lightweight eco-friendly 3/4-shell mountain bike eMTB helmet, Pop-Off visor\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-with-Pop-Off-visor-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-with-Pop-Off-visor-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-with-Pop-Off-visor-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-with-Pop-Off-visor-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-with-Pop-Off-visor-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_side-with-Pop-Off-visor-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>2 position adjustable Pop-Off visor designed to fit goggles and tear away in a crash</li>\n\n\n\n<li>sunglasses garage under the visor</li>\n\n\n\n<li>wrap-around ear padding reduces wind noise, while also enabling natural cooling</li>\n\n\n\n<li>available in 2 sizes with adjustable fit: S/M (54-58cm) or L/XL (58-62cm)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>EU safety tested to EN 1078:2012+A1:2013 standard for MTB  &amp; eBike use</li>\n\n\n\n<li>weights from 420g for the smaller helmet or also from 480g for the larger one</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Urge Rascas MTB helmet – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_up-close-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_up-close-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Urge Rascas lightweight eco-friendly 3/4-shell mountain bike eMTB helmet, side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_up-close-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_up-close-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_up-close-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_up-close-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_up-close-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_up-close-2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_up-close-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_up-close-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The all-new Urge Rascas 3/4 shell (Jet-style) helmet sells for 199€ and is <a href=\"https://urgebike.com/en/product/rascas-dark-moon-ert/\" target=\"_blank\">available now</a>, directly from Urge. It comes in two sizes S/M or L/XL. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_colors-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_colors-jpg.webp\" alt=\"Urge Rascas lightweight eco-friendly 3/4-shell mountain bike eMTB helmet, colors\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_colors-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_colors-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_colors-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_colors-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_colors-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_colors-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Urge-Rascas-lightweight-eco-friendly-three-quarter-shell-mountain-bike-eMTB-helmet_colors-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Then, pick from 4 different color combinations, all with 