 to come.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://urgebike.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>UrgeBike.com</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/urge-rascas-lightens-up-eco-friendly-3-4-shell-mtb-helmet-for-enduro-emtb-riders/\">Urge Rascas Lightens Up Eco-Friendly 3/4-Shell MTB Helmet for Enduro &amp; eMTB Riders</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"1d8be8a6653aab4ebc6dcb5ef0cbead363180c88e3113a7cf60694ac42fa10f3","category":"Cycling"}